text: Belgacem Bouguenna () is a Tunisian singer and teacher, born in Douz (Kebili). ==Discography== * El Walda ( Mother.) * El Ghorba (Exile.) * Fatma (His lover's name.) * Wras 3youni (I swear on my eyes.) ==References== ==External links== * Belgacem Bouguenna blog * Bouguenna songs Category:Tunisian male singers Category:Living people Category:21st-century Tunisian people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Belgacem Bouguenna
